{"name":"Aloo Gobi","slug":"aloo-gobi","description":"<p>Crispy vegetables sautéed in warm aromatic spices. Dinner is solved. &nbsp;</p>","ingredients":[{"name":"medium russet potato","quantity":"1","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"cauliflower florets","quantity":"4 cups","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"lentils","quantity":"1 can (19 oz/540 ml)","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"oil","quantity":"2 <sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>2</sub> tbsp","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"Aloo Gobi Seasoning","quantity":"1 pkg","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"water","quantity":"<sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>2</sub> cup","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"tomato paste","quantity":"2 tbsp","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"frozen peas","quantity":"<sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>2</sub> cup","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"plain 2% Greek yogurt","quantity":"2 cups","additionalInstruction":null}],"totalTime":"20 min","servings":"4 servings","preparation":"<ol>\n  <li>Peel and dice potato into small cubes. Place in <a data-item-id=\"bd092c36-a4ba-5b73-9abc-fa95c0102e9a\" href=\"\">Multipurpose Steamer</a> with cauliflower. Cover and microwave on high 5–6 min, until almost tender.</li>\n  <li>Meanwhile, drain and rinse lentils.</li>\n  <li>Heat oil in <a data-item-id=\"4592bb8a-4986-4f89-8253-3ff61af8d78e\" href=\"\">Sauté Pan</a> over medium-high heat. Add seasoning; stir until fragrant, 45 sec. Add cooked potatoes and cauliflower; stir to coat.</li>\n  <li>Add lentils, water, and tomato paste. Reduce to simmer. Cover and cook for 8–10 min, or until potatoes are tender.</li>\n  <li>Stir in peas; cook for 1–2 min.</li>\n  <li>Divide into four bowls and top each with <sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>2</sub> cup yogurt and chopped cilantro, if desired.</li>\n</ol>","tags":[{"slug":"epic_life_lunch","name":"Lunch"},{"slug":"low_sodium","name":"Low-sodium"},{"slug":"sugar_conscious","name":"Sugar Conscious"},{"slug":"one_dish","name":"One Dish"},{"slug":"dinner","name":"Di